1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,539
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,539 --> 00:01:38,020
Episode 27

3
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:59,050
I

4
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:01,330
really had a family mishap.

5
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:04,170
My wife has no morality or manners

6
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,890
and messed up Mr. Shang’s The Tale of Dragon,

7
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:10,729
of which I’m deeply ashamed.

8
00:02:10,860 --> 00:02:11,690
That’s an overstatement.

9
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:15,020
I came to make an apology

10
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:16,079
(Old Mountain Wild Ginseng)
I came to make an apology

11
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:16,240
(Old Mountain Wild Ginseng)

12
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,430
with a humble gift today.
(Old Mountain Wild Ginseng)

13
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:20,490
Hope you can forgive me, Mr. Shang.

14
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:22,610
Please also tell Mr. Cheng

15
00:02:22,620 --> 00:02:23,810
and Mr. Fan.

16
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:25,010
that I’m sorry.

17
00:02:25,940 --> 00:02:26,810
No problem.

18
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:28,170
No problem.

19
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:35,920
Well…

20
00:02:37,180 --> 00:02:38,010
Yu Qing,

21
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:41,579
Miss Yu,

22
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,040
refused to see me.

23
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:48,410
Is she doing well?

24
00:02:52,730 --> 00:02:53,740
Yu Qing…

25
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:03,450
Miss Yu has the temperament of a scholar.

26
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:08,810
When you judged her like that in public,

27
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,270
she felt so desperate.

28
00:03:15,770 --> 00:03:17,690
There’s no doing well to speak of.

29
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:23,810
Mr. Yuan, if you really sympathize with her,

30
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:27,290
you shouldn’t have come to see her.

31
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:31,300
She…

32
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:33,690
She said from now on,

33
00:03:35,780 --> 00:03:37,490
she’d never sing operas again.

34
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:41,890
She followed you

35
00:03:42,780 --> 00:03:44,530
and left home,

36
00:03:45,370 --> 00:03:47,530
following you to sing on the stage,

37
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,890
now she ends up with nothing,

38
00:03:51,380 --> 00:03:52,820
and has no families around.

39
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:57,370
What should she do in the days to come?

40
00:04:11,900 --> 00:04:12,690
I’ll take leave,

41
00:04:13,100 --> 00:04:13,890
Mr. Shang.

42
00:04:25,060 --> 00:04:26,050
Did you see that? Did you see that?

43
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:26,650
That son of a bitch cried!

44
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:27,450
It serves him right!

45
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:29,210
That was quite a game of bluff of yours.

46
00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:29,850
Come on, come on.

47
00:04:30,020 --> 00:04:31,050
Let me have a look.

48
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:33,290
-Where did you get your tears from?
-Here.

49
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:37,050
Find a pawn to cash in the stuff he sent

50
00:04:37,260 --> 00:04:38,090
and give the cash to Yu Qing.

51
00:04:38,790 --> 00:04:40,010
Give money for no reason.

52
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:40,970
How’s that going to come about?

53
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:44,490
Just say she got implicated into tabloid news,

54
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:46,520
and this is a compensation

55
00:04:46,530 --> 00:04:48,010
for her mental distress from her rumored lover.

56
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:55,570
Sir, I’m grateful to your great favor of rescue

57
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,210
and taking me in as your disciple.

58
00:05:58,020 --> 00:05:59,730
You have such consummate skill

59
00:06:00,420 --> 00:06:01,730
that I have nothing to repay your kindness.

60
00:06:03,020 --> 00:06:04,290
I can only bone up on it

61
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:05,530
to get a ten thousandth of it

62
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:09,290
so that I won’t live my life in vain.

63
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:13,410
Everybody present is my witness.

64
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,530
I took you in as my apprentice

65
00:06:39,050 --> 00:06:39,930
not to get reciprocation

66
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:41,650
but to pass on my skills.

67
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:44,210
You must remember what you said today.

68
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,370
Practice diligently every day

69
00:06:45,909 --> 00:06:46,860
and don’t slack off.

70
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,890
Mr. Shang spoke like a book,

71
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:53,409
he really has the air of a master.

72
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:56,340
(Party A: Cheng Fengtai. Party B: Zhou Xiangyun.)

73
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:02,690
Mr. Cheng.

74
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:08,010
Mr. Cheng,

75
00:07:08,210 --> 00:07:09,130
please come out for a while.

76
00:07:18,930 --> 00:07:20,170
Zeng Aiyu is about to give birth.

77
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:21,170
What’s to be done?

78
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:21,890
What?

79
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:24,170
So suddenly?

80
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:27,130
Aren’t there still some days before the due date?

81
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:28,370
Where is Fan Lian?

82
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:29,210
I’ve looked for him.

83
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:30,250
I heard he’s gone

84
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:33,450
to Hangzhou to buy costumes and paraphernalia.

85
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:36,650
That bastard

86
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:39,330
must have made an excuse to get away.

87
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:41,290
Let’s go to the hospital.

88
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:43,570
Madam,

89
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:45,730
we’d better go to the hospital.

90
00:07:46,380 --> 00:07:47,330
-What’s wrong with her?
-Mr. Cheng.

91
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:49,490
She keeps feeling pain in her belly.

92
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:51,170
I ask her to go to the hospital, but she won’t go.

93
00:07:51,820 --> 00:07:53,290
The little baby in my belly

94
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:55,450
keeps turning and tossing day and night.

95
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:57,130
It’s killing me.

96
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:00,050
From what it’s doing,

97
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:01,290
probably

98
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:04,810
it’ll take my life to have its life.

99
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,170
Don’t say disheartening things.

100
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:08,650
Aren’t you going to take the money with you

101
00:08:08,660 --> 00:08:09,890
to save your families?

102
00:08:10,780 --> 00:08:11,810
My families…

103
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:16,560
Go and get ready.

104
00:08:16,590 --> 00:08:17,130
Let’s go to the hospital.

105
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:17,530
OK.

106
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:18,490
Let’s go.

107
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:19,570
No, no need.

108
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:20,980
No, I don’t need to go to the hospital.

109
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,350
I’m having throbbing pains.

110
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:23,490
I’ll be OK

111
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:25,530
when the bout of pain passes.

112
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:27,090
I really don’t need to go to the hospital.

113
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:28,450
It’s hard to say when it comes to childbirth.

114
00:08:28,740 --> 00:08:29,530
What if it’ll be a premature birth?

115
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,210
Be obedient.

116
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:31,210
If it’s a premature birth,

117
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:34,850
it’ll cost my life and the baby’s,

118
00:08:37,929 --> 00:08:38,770
and happen to

119
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:42,330
save a hundred thousand yuan for you.

120
00:08:42,929 --> 00:08:44,210
What’s a hundred thousand yuan worth

121
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:45,650
compared with the safety of you and your baby?

122
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:48,410
Come on.

123
00:08:48,710 --> 00:08:49,370
Hold on to me.

124
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:50,490
Come on.

125
00:08:51,180 --> 00:08:51,730
OK.

126
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:56,330
Call the hospital

127
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:57,090
and ask them to make preparations.

128
00:08:57,820 --> 00:08:58,850
Keep contacting Fan Lian

129
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:01,410
and don’t stop until you find him.

130
00:09:01,690 --> 00:09:02,090
OK.

131
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,610
My belly aches.

132
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:20,850
My… my belly…

133
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:22,610
My belly has burst.

134
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:24,810
Mr. Cheng,

135
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:26,810
can you hold me in your arms?

136
00:09:26,820 --> 00:09:27,250
Mr. Cheng…

137
00:09:34,650 --> 00:09:35,330
It’s OK. It’s OK.

138
00:09:36,700 --> 00:09:37,810
Your water broke.

139
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:40,450
My wife has given birth.

140
00:09:40,780 --> 00:09:41,530
I know better than you.

141
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:43,330
It’s OK.

142
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:44,890
Don’t be afraid. Don’t be afraid.

143
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:46,650
Mr. Cheng,

144
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:50,890
can you hold me tighter?

145
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:09,730
It’s a premature birth.

146
00:10:09,940 --> 00:10:10,850
Fortunately, she was sent here in time,

147
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,050
otherwise there will be serious consequences.

148
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:13,810
Go and pay to get a medical expense list first.

149
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,490
OK.

150
00:10:16,020 --> 00:10:23,580
(Keep Quiet. Authorized Personnel Only.)

151
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:26,950
You don’t have to worry too much.

152
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,550
The fetal position is quite normal,

153
00:10:28,740 --> 00:10:29,470
and the fetus

154
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,470
is growing very well.

155
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:32,230
Take a moderate amount of walk during these days,

156
00:10:32,310 --> 00:10:33,150
pay attention to intake of nutrition,

157
00:10:33,380 --> 00:10:34,930
and you can leave after a few days’ observation.

158
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:37,210
That’s great then.

159
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,970
Thank you, doctor.

160
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,090
It’s all right.

161
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:41,570
Let me know at any time if you need me.

162
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,410
Thanks.

163
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,330
Have a good rest.

164
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:44,610
Let’s go.

165
00:11:02,650 --> 00:11:03,210
Be careful.

166
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:09,730
Here, be careful.

167
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:18,580
-You must have a good rest.
-Thanks.

168
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,650
Let the nurse know if you need anything.

169
00:11:21,300 --> 00:11:23,010
Let us know even if you have

170
00:11:23,020 --> 00:11:23,930
the slightest discomfort.

171
00:11:24,090 --> 00:11:25,050
We are on call at any time.

172
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:26,330
Thank you.

173
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:32,930
Thanks.

174
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:42,370
Would you like some porridge?

175
00:11:42,660 --> 00:11:43,770
I have some more here.

176
00:11:44,660 --> 00:11:45,610
No, thanks.

177
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:47,490
I’ve just had a surgery,

178
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:49,530
and the doctor doesn’t allow me to eat.

179
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:56,890
Have you just had a baby?

180
00:12:01,820 --> 00:12:02,730
I saw

181
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:03,970
some pregnant women before

182
00:12:04,340 --> 00:12:05,450
who looked as if

183
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:06,890
they lost half of their lives after childbirth.

184
00:12:08,020 --> 00:12:10,330
I’ve never seen anybody as spirited as you.

185
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:13,210
The doctor said the same thing.

186
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:16,370
But only I myself know

187
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:19,770
how much I suffered during delivery.

188
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:26,570
If only

189
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:29,050
Wish I could deliver a baby smoothly.

190
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,170
From the way you look,

191
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:33,900
I’m sure you’ll be fine.

192
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:36,530
Miss,

193
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:38,090
please elaborate on

194
00:12:38,430 --> 00:12:39,730
the dos and don’ts.

195
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:40,690
I’m all ears.

196
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:43,490
What is he saying?

197
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:45,570
Stop dawdling

198
00:12:45,770 --> 00:12:46,730
and come in.

199
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:56,490
Is it your husband who’s talking outside the door?

200
00:13:01,130 --> 00:13:02,330
Yes.

201
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:06,240
He has the temper of a young master of the Bund.

202
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:07,330
Look,

203
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:10,010
I’m suffering here

204
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,210
while

205
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:14,730
he’s showing the swagger of a master outside.

206
00:13:19,980 --> 00:13:21,130
I’m going to the bathroom.

207
00:13:29,780 --> 00:13:31,730
The gynecologist is busier than a committee chair.

208
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:33,610
I waited quite some time to get the prescription.

209
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:37,170
Stop walking around.

210
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:38,810
Stay here for a while.

211
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:40,610
As a man,

212
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:42,650
I stick out like a sore thumb staying here.

213
00:13:43,260 --> 00:13:44,770
The housemaid is cooking ginseng soup for you.

214
00:13:44,780 --> 00:13:45,570
She’ll bring it to you later.

215
00:13:46,140 --> 00:13:47,930
Go to bed early when you finish it.

216
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,050
I’ve got something else to do, I’m off.

217
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:55,370
The nurse will come with the baby later.

218
00:13:56,140 --> 00:13:57,290
Don’t you want to have a look?

219
00:13:57,660 --> 00:13:58,730
A boy or a girl?

220
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:02,850
A girl.

221
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:05,650
That’s just right.

222
00:14:06,010 --> 00:14:07,010
I have a son,

223
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:08,330
and you have a daughter.

224
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,330
That makes a pair of children.

225
00:14:10,860 --> 00:14:12,010
I must have a look then.

226
00:14:12,020 --> 00:14:13,210
Zeng Aiyu’s family,

227
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:14,490
the doctor has an instruction for you.

228
00:14:16,740 --> 00:14:17,730
I’ll go and have a look.

229
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:18,490
I’m coming.

230
00:14:37,140 --> 00:14:37,650
Are you

231
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:39,170
unwell?

232
00:14:42,190 --> 00:14:42,690
No.

233
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:45,490
It’s quite cold here at night.

234
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:47,410
I’ll go and call my family

235
00:14:47,620 --> 00:14:49,650
to bring an extra quilt here.

236
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:46,530
Mrs. Cheng,

237
00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:47,610
here’s a letter.

238
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:52,670
Look.

239
00:15:53,380 --> 00:15:54,010
Isn’t this fun?
(To: Cheng Fengtai. From Chunxuan)

240
00:15:54,010 --> 00:15:54,620
(To: Cheng Fengtai. From Chunxuan)

241
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:56,490
Chunxuan.

242
00:15:59,060 --> 00:16:00,010
Good boy.

243
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:06,170
Here, be careful.

244
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:09,170
Mrs. Cheng,

245
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:10,850
you have a call from Mengping.

246
00:16:13,260 --> 00:16:13,730
Here you are.

247
00:16:16,620 --> 00:16:17,570
Be careful, be careful.

248
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:18,660
Little young master.

249
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:21,930
Hello.

250
00:16:22,380 --> 00:16:23,290
Mengping,

251
00:16:24,140 --> 00:16:25,390
how are you?

252
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:27,890
What prompts you to call me?

253
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:29,490
Xiang’er,

254
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:30,970
I…

255
00:16:31,740 --> 00:16:32,970
I… I’m doing well.

256
00:16:34,580 --> 00:16:36,010
I’m actually calling you about nothing.

257
00:16:36,190 --> 00:16:36,810
I just…

258
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:44,410
Just what?

259
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:45,850
Hello,

260
00:16:46,370 --> 00:16:47,250
Mengping?

261
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:53,090
Xiang’er,

262
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:56,610
I saw a man in the hospital.

263
00:17:14,099 --> 00:17:14,720
Mrs. Cheng,

264
00:17:15,060 --> 00:17:16,200
what’s wrong with you, Mrs. Cheng?

265
00:17:17,109 --> 00:17:19,240
Are you unwell, Mrs. Cheng?

266
00:17:20,010 --> 00:17:21,450
What’s wrong with you, Mrs. Cheng?

267
00:17:24,490 --> 00:17:25,240
Someone, please!

268
00:17:25,540 --> 00:17:27,720
Someone! Mrs. Cheng is unwell.

269
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,090
What’s wrong, Mrs. Cheng?

270
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:32,650
Mrs. Cheng.

271
00:17:33,820 --> 00:17:35,010
Mrs. Cheng, what’s wrong with you?

272
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:35,850
What’s going on?

273
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:38,290
Xiang… Xiang’er,

274
00:17:38,740 --> 00:17:40,090
what…what’s going on?

275
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:41,330
I don’t know.

276
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:43,290
Say something, Xiang’er.

277
00:17:43,820 --> 00:17:44,730
What’s the matter?

278
00:17:46,740 --> 00:17:47,370
Xiang’er.

279
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:49,410
Step aside, step aside.

280
00:17:49,700 --> 00:17:50,210
Don’t block the way.

281
00:17:51,820 --> 00:17:52,250
Hurry up.

282
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:54,770
-Go and get the storax oil from my room.
-OK.

283
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:56,410
Mrs. Cheng, what’s wrong with you?

284
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:58,250
Say something, Mrs. Cheng.

285
00:17:59,020 --> 00:17:59,770
Chunxing,

286
00:17:59,980 --> 00:18:00,850
what happened?

287
00:18:00,860 --> 00:18:01,770
I’ve no idea.

288
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:04,610
Hurry up, Chunxing,

289
00:18:04,700 --> 00:18:05,930
let Mrs. Cheng smell it.

290
00:18:06,060 --> 00:18:07,090
Also apply some on her temples.

291
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:08,930
Get out.

292
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:11,410
Everybody get out.

293
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:13,130
Hurry up. Get out, get out.

294
00:18:13,140 --> 00:18:14,010
Do what Mrs. Cheng says.

295
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:15,210
Everybody get out.

296
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:16,410
Hurry up, get out.

297
00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:18,850
Get out.

298
00:18:19,060 --> 00:18:19,770
Let’s go.

299
00:18:24,820 --> 00:18:25,580
Go.

300
00:18:26,210 --> 00:18:26,890
Go on with your work.

301
00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:37,530
Just scold my younger brother if he did anything wrong.

302
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:40,170
Why bother yourself like this?

303
00:18:43,460 --> 00:18:45,290
But he’s been keeping a mistress behind my back,

304
00:18:45,580 --> 00:18:47,810
and they’ve even had a baby!

305
00:18:48,020 --> 00:18:49,850
He tried so hard to keep it from me!

306
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:05,690
Very good.

307
00:19:06,100 --> 00:19:07,450
She looks like Fan Lian a lot.

308
00:19:11,220 --> 00:19:12,170
In what way?

309
00:19:13,220 --> 00:19:14,010
I think

310
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:15,650
she looks like you a lot.

311
00:19:18,660 --> 00:19:19,930
Don’t talk nonsense.

312
00:19:21,780 --> 00:19:23,250
If only it were you

313
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:26,260
who fell for me back then!

314
00:19:27,260 --> 00:19:29,250
Then I certainly wouldn’t make you pregnant,

315
00:19:30,570 --> 00:19:31,370
and there wouldn’t be

316
00:19:31,380 --> 00:19:32,890
such a cute baby now.

317
00:19:34,740 --> 00:19:35,690
Take your time to recuperate.

318
00:19:36,580 --> 00:19:37,730
I’ve really got to go.

319
00:19:38,460 --> 00:19:39,850
When Fan Lian comes back from Hangzhou,

320
00:19:40,340 --> 00:19:41,570
I’ll ask him to come over to see you.

321
00:19:42,010 --> 00:19:43,010
Don’t ask him to come.

322
00:19:43,980 --> 00:19:44,970
I don’t want to see him.

323
00:19:47,380 --> 00:19:48,530
It is between you and Fan Lian

324
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:50,250
to fall out and break up.

325
00:19:51,130 --> 00:19:53,170
You should let the father see his baby.

326
00:19:56,130 --> 00:19:56,930
When I leave

327
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:01,130
and the baby falls into his hands,

328
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:05,050
he can see her for as long as he likes.

329
00:20:15,900 --> 00:20:16,490
By the way,

330
00:20:17,700 --> 00:20:19,610
I opened an account for you with the CitiBank.

331
00:20:20,100 --> 00:20:21,570
I’ve transferred money into it.

332
00:20:21,940 --> 00:20:23,410
I’ll bring you the deposit book tomorrow.

333
00:20:30,060 --> 00:20:30,690
OK.

334
00:21:03,180 --> 00:21:03,690
Hold on.

335
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:04,570
Mr. Cheng is back.

336
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:05,930
Mr. Cheng, Mr. Cheng!

337
00:21:06,420 --> 00:21:07,810
You have a call from Chacha’er.

338
00:21:07,900 --> 00:21:08,730
She’s called quite a few times.

339
00:21:11,740 --> 00:21:12,610
Hi, Chacha’er.

340
00:21:13,010 --> 00:21:13,690
What’s the matter?

341
00:21:13,900 --> 00:21:15,210
Brother, be quick to come home.

342
00:21:15,430 --> 00:21:16,530
Xiang’er has known what happened to you.

343
00:21:17,180 --> 00:21:17,930
What?

344
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:20,690
She has known you have a love child.

345
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:26,530
Hello.

346
00:21:28,490 --> 00:21:29,130
Hello?

347
00:21:39,630 --> 00:21:40,450
Xiang’er,

348
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:43,610
my younger brother is 100% faithful to you.

349
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:45,890
You can’t get him wrong.

350
00:21:46,460 --> 00:21:47,570
All right, all right.

351
00:21:49,140 --> 00:21:50,970
As you know about men,

352
00:21:51,580 --> 00:21:53,640
it’s common for them to run errands

353
00:21:53,700 --> 00:21:54,770
for each other.

354
00:21:54,860 --> 00:21:57,050
They also look after each other’s mistresses.

355
00:21:58,500 --> 00:21:59,470
Most of those women

356
00:22:00,020 --> 00:22:01,690
come from seedy backgrounds.

357
00:22:02,140 --> 00:22:04,610
They have no scruples after seeing many men.

358
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:06,440
Maybe the one your sister-in-law saw

359
00:22:06,510 --> 00:22:08,930
is one of my younger brother’s friends’ mistress.

360
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:10,290
Right?

361
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:11,890
You can’t

362
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:14,250
throw such a thing at him willy-nilly.

363
00:22:14,420 --> 00:22:15,050
All right, all right.

364
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:16,690
When my younger brother is back,

365
00:22:16,820 --> 00:22:17,770
if he can’t explain it clearly,

366
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:19,010
I’ll get back at him for you.

367
00:22:19,660 --> 00:22:20,410
OK?

368
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:22,200
Stop crying.

369
00:22:22,580 --> 00:22:23,290
Mrs. Cheng,

370
00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:24,330
Mrs. Cao,

371
00:22:24,770 --> 00:22:25,650
Mr. Cheng is back.

372
00:22:26,610 --> 00:22:27,370
He’s back.

373
00:22:27,820 --> 00:22:28,530
He’s back.

374
00:22:29,180 --> 00:22:30,210
Ask him about it.

375
00:22:35,360 --> 00:22:36,250
Both of you are in?

376
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:44,170
What happened?

377
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,650
You both have a serious look.

378
00:22:48,460 --> 00:22:49,290
Sit down.

379
00:22:58,580 --> 00:22:59,730
Where is my coffee?

380
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:01,490
Fengtai,

381
00:23:03,620 --> 00:23:05,330
I don’t care whose baby it is,

382
00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:08,090
it’s just not right for you

383
00:23:08,260 --> 00:23:09,290
to have a finger in the pie.

384
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:11,170
Be quick

385
00:23:11,760 --> 00:23:13,050
to apologize to your wife

386
00:23:13,300 --> 00:23:15,170
and explain the ins and outs of it to her.

387
00:23:20,020 --> 00:23:21,570
Turns out this is what you are worrying about.

388
00:23:22,940 --> 00:23:23,770
Then I’m wrong.

389
00:23:24,530 --> 00:23:25,570
I’m really wrong.

390
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:28,330
I shouldn’t have minded Fan Lian’s business.

391
00:23:30,260 --> 00:23:31,890
You even blame Fan Lian for it?

392
00:23:33,130 --> 00:23:34,930
He’s a bachelor.

393
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:36,650
Why does he refuse to claim his

394
00:23:37,020 --> 00:23:38,050
ties with the baby?

395
00:23:39,180 --> 00:23:39,690
Go!

396
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,210
-Go!
-There there.

397
00:23:42,220 --> 00:23:43,330
You have a family outside.

398
00:23:43,340 --> 00:23:44,960
There’s no place for you in this family!

399
00:23:50,700 --> 00:23:51,930
There there.

400
00:23:53,140 --> 00:23:53,770
Mrs. Cheng,

401
00:23:53,780 --> 00:23:54,410
don’t get worked up.

402
00:23:55,260 --> 00:23:56,210
Don’t cry. Don’t cry.

403
00:23:56,420 --> 00:23:56,930
Don’t cry.

404
00:23:57,660 --> 00:23:58,210
Don’t cry.

405
00:23:59,540 --> 00:24:01,010
Take a sip of water to cool down.

406
00:24:08,220 --> 00:24:09,330
When you cool down,

407
00:24:10,180 --> 00:24:12,250
I’ll explain it to you from A to Z.

408
00:24:15,340 --> 00:24:16,890
Leave the seal behind when you go.

409
00:24:19,980 --> 00:24:22,410
The Cheng family got all its money from our Fan family.

410
00:24:23,220 --> 00:24:24,950
Why are you showing such swagger?

411
00:24:25,820 --> 00:24:26,610
I tell you what,

412
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:28,530
don’t think of taking even a cent with you

413
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:29,970
to spend it on your mistress!

414
00:24:31,060 --> 00:24:32,210
If you’ve got any spunk in you,

415
00:24:32,420 --> 00:24:33,210
just get out of the house empty-handed.

416
00:24:33,860 --> 00:24:34,730
What did you say?

417
00:24:35,860 --> 00:24:38,490
The Cheng family got all its money from your Fan family?

418
00:24:39,780 --> 00:24:41,700
Turns out that’s what you think all the time.

419
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:43,730
Fengtai,

420
00:24:44,260 --> 00:24:45,730
Xiang’er is angry now.

421
00:24:45,780 --> 00:24:46,930
She was talking nonsense.

422
00:24:48,260 --> 00:24:48,850
Xiang’er,

423
00:24:49,380 --> 00:24:50,970
how can my younger brother have another family?

424
00:24:51,290 --> 00:24:52,290
His family

425
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:53,410
is here.

426
00:24:56,580 --> 00:24:57,530
Let him go.

427
00:24:58,340 --> 00:24:59,810
He has more than one family.

428
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:01,650
This woman gave birth to his child,

429
00:25:01,900 --> 00:25:03,590
and that woman sent a letter home.

430
00:25:04,360 --> 00:25:05,490
Chunxuan, isn’t she?

431
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:07,340
All right.

432
00:25:08,060 --> 00:25:09,250
You are quite a playboy.

433
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:11,090
No wonder you don’t want to stay home.

434
00:25:11,940 --> 00:25:12,730
Your lovers outside

435
00:25:12,740 --> 00:25:14,490
can line up to see you on different days!

436
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:17,250
Whom did you say?

437
00:25:19,260 --> 00:25:20,330
Look at you.

438
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:22,090
Didn’t I get it right?

439
00:25:24,700 --> 00:25:25,250
Where’s the letter?

440
00:25:26,300 --> 00:25:27,290
Where is the letter?

441
00:25:27,940 --> 00:25:29,090
It was burnt in the kitchen.

442
00:25:31,360 --> 00:25:32,010
Fengtai!

443
00:25:32,260 --> 00:25:32,960
Look.

444
00:25:33,340 --> 00:25:34,890
Look how nervous he is!

445
00:25:37,140 --> 00:25:38,330
All right, Xiang’er,

446
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:41,290
I dare not be certain about the baby,

447
00:25:41,620 --> 00:25:44,770
but you’ve indeed blamed him wrongly.

448
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:48,720
Chunxuan

449
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:50,810
is his real mother.

450
00:25:54,190 --> 00:25:56,530
Few people know about it.

451
00:26:07,340 --> 00:26:13,780
(Chunxuan)

452
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:38,570
After looking for her for over a decade,

453
00:26:40,580 --> 00:26:42,490
I’d just heard from her

454
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:47,330
and you just ruined it.

455
00:27:20,100 --> 00:27:20,970
Fengtai,

456
00:27:21,450 --> 00:27:22,970
stay cool when you have something to say.

457
00:27:22,980 --> 00:27:24,410
What are you doing this for?

458
00:27:45,860 --> 00:27:47,490
That damn Cao Wanjun.

459
00:27:47,580 --> 00:27:49,090
He has money to burn

460
00:27:49,380 --> 00:27:50,810
but just won’t pay the debts for me.

461
00:27:54,060 --> 00:27:56,130
I asked you to write a letter to that spinster in Fanjiabao.

462
00:27:56,180 --> 00:27:57,090
Did you write it?

463
00:27:59,180 --> 00:27:59,690
Yes, I did.

464
00:28:00,660 --> 00:28:01,760
That’s more like it.

465
00:28:03,140 --> 00:28:04,370
I hope her dowry

466
00:28:04,900 --> 00:28:07,130
can pay our family’s debts.

467
00:28:07,140 --> 00:28:08,450
I told her in the letter

468
00:28:09,820 --> 00:28:11,410
that I don’t want to make her my wife.

469
00:28:13,020 --> 00:28:14,880
Do you want to die, Cheng Fengtai?

470
00:28:16,180 --> 00:28:17,050
I tell you what,

471
00:28:17,260 --> 00:28:18,650
it’s not up to you whether to marry or not.

472
00:28:18,660 --> 00:28:19,610
That’s a marriage arranged when you were a kid.

473
00:28:20,140 --> 00:28:21,010
What’s more,

474
00:28:21,540 --> 00:28:22,330
if you don’t marry her,

475
00:28:22,570 --> 00:28:23,730
what shall our Cheng family do?

476
00:28:23,740 --> 00:28:24,850
What’s to be done to our debts?

477
00:28:26,860 --> 00:28:28,410
At worst, sell the Cheng’s residence

478
00:28:28,700 --> 00:28:29,890
and move to a smaller house.

479
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:36,730
You are out of your mind, aren’t you, Cheng Fengtai?

480
00:28:37,430 --> 00:28:38,490
If this house is sold,

481
00:28:38,700 --> 00:28:39,890
how can there still be the Cheng family?

482
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:41,470
-Brother, help!
-Knock it off!

483
00:28:41,690 --> 00:28:42,610
-Let go of her.
-Let go of me!

484
00:28:42,860 --> 00:28:44,410
Brother, help! Piss off!

485
00:28:44,420 --> 00:28:45,090
Get out of here.

486
00:28:46,980 --> 00:28:47,690
What are you doing?

487
00:28:49,380 --> 00:28:50,370
Since we can’t sell the house,

488
00:28:51,940 --> 00:28:53,050
we have no choice but to sell her.

489
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:54,010
Are you insane?

490
00:28:54,540 --> 00:28:54,930
You can’t!

491
00:28:55,700 --> 00:28:56,970
No matter who Chacha’er’s mother is,

492
00:28:57,500 --> 00:28:59,090
she is father’s own daughter

493
00:28:59,270 --> 00:29:00,490
and our own younger sister.

494
00:29:00,580 --> 00:29:02,210
It’s too late to say no now.

495
00:29:02,740 --> 00:29:03,970
I’ve taken the money.

496
00:29:04,540 --> 00:29:05,610
If you refuse,

497
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:07,090
raise money for them yourself.

498
00:29:11,300 --> 00:29:13,130
Then I’ll go to see that girl surnamed Fan

499
00:29:14,310 --> 00:29:15,410
and ask her to be my wife.

500
00:29:16,060 --> 00:29:17,050
Does that make you happy?

501
00:29:22,820 --> 00:29:23,450
Mr. Cheng,

502
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:25,490
we’ve been driving round and round,

503
00:29:26,230 --> 00:29:27,330
where are we going?

504
00:29:35,740 --> 00:29:36,650
To the Shuiyun Theater.

505
00:29:37,140 --> 00:29:37,770
OK.

506
00:30:01,750 --> 00:30:02,330
Sister,

507
00:30:03,060 --> 00:30:04,530
are you really going to Shanghai?

508
00:30:05,390 --> 00:30:06,490
The brat of the Cheng family

509
00:30:06,620 --> 00:30:07,730
looked down on me at first

510
00:30:08,230 --> 00:30:09,510
by sending me a letter to cancel our engagement,

511
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:12,090
now he wrote another letter to coax me into marrying him.

512
00:30:12,730 --> 00:30:13,250
Needless to ask,

513
00:30:13,600 --> 00:30:14,570
he must be short of money.

514
00:30:15,470 --> 00:30:16,490
With ill intentions,

515
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,690
he’s been coveting my dowry.

516
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:20,270
Are you still going while you know that?

517
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:21,690
As a dignified maiden of the Fan family,

518
00:30:21,740 --> 00:30:23,050
how can I be jerked around by him like this?

519
00:30:23,920 --> 00:30:26,210
I’ll just go with my money to put him to shame,

520
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,730
dangle it in front of him

521
00:30:29,040 --> 00:30:30,010
and have my revenge.

522
00:30:30,620 --> 00:30:35,210
♬ I suddenly look back while being caught off guard ♬

523
00:30:36,040 --> 00:30:40,710
♬ I pretend to muddle along as if nothing matters ♬

524
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:44,060
♬ A bud blossoms from the dust ♬

525
00:30:44,060 --> 00:30:47,030
(Greeting the bride)
♬ A bud blossoms from the dust ♬

526
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:47,510
(Greeting the bride)

527
00:30:47,510 --> 00:30:48,060
♬ I do not regret ♬
(Greeting the bride)

528
00:30:48,060 --> 00:30:50,850
♬ I do not regret ♬

529
00:30:50,890 --> 00:30:56,360
♬ Going through wind and snow with you Drink it up♬

530
00:30:56,600 --> 00:31:02,520
♬ Our souls face each other in the operas I’m a bit ashamed ♬

531
00:31:02,550 --> 00:31:07,950
♬ I didn’t say but you understand it telepathically Just get drunk ♬

532
00:31:07,980 --> 00:31:13,040
♬ You told me in the dream it’s such a beautiful world ♬

533
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:18,560
♬ A period of our time in life can only be sensed
No comfort needed ♬

534
00:31:18,590 --> 00:31:21,760
♬ Both of us know to forget with a broken heart ♬

535
00:31:22,150 --> 00:31:22,970
Are you in a daze?

536
00:31:24,290 --> 00:31:29,410
♬ Every minute and second is not enough to experience ♬

537
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,110
♬ Enchanting lush mountains ♬

538
00:31:31,220 --> 00:31:34,230
♬ Looking back at the stage ♬

539
00:31:35,850 --> 00:31:37,330
Are you still feeling bad?

540
00:31:42,620 --> 00:31:43,850
I’m in the wrong.

541
00:31:44,500 --> 00:31:45,650
It’s not your fault.

542
00:31:47,260 --> 00:31:48,810
My younger brother’s mother Chunxuan

543
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:51,530
is an old memory.

544
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:53,770
Few people know about her.

545
00:31:54,580 --> 00:31:55,770
Would you like to hear anything about her?

546
00:32:01,380 --> 00:32:02,690
I was young back then,

547
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:06,610
but she left

548
00:32:07,860 --> 00:32:09,570
such a deep impression on me.

549
00:32:10,900 --> 00:32:13,010
How Chunxuan got into the Cheng family,

550
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:14,490
I can’t remember.

551
00:32:16,580 --> 00:32:18,930
I can only remember her beauty and charm,

552
00:32:20,460 --> 00:32:22,610
accompanied with colorful costumes

553
00:32:23,020 --> 00:32:24,730
and glittering jewelries.

554
00:32:26,300 --> 00:32:28,130
I was very close to her back then,

555
00:32:29,580 --> 00:32:31,330
as I thought she was very pretty.

556
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,210
Little did I realize

557
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:35,610
her beauty

558
00:32:36,380 --> 00:32:39,930
was out of kilter with the Cheng family.

559
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:46,010
Well, Chunxuan,

560
00:32:46,460 --> 00:32:49,210
now you’ve got into our Cheng family by a happy chance,

561
00:32:49,220 --> 00:32:50,370
you’ve given birth

562
00:32:50,460 --> 00:32:51,730
and you’ve got status,

563
00:32:51,820 --> 00:32:54,650
whom do you want to show these coquettish tricks to?

564
00:32:55,340 --> 00:32:56,130
Mom,

565
00:32:56,580 --> 00:32:57,730
as you said,

566
00:32:58,180 --> 00:32:59,650
I’ve given birth,

567
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:02,610
can’t I sing operas at home with the door shut?

568
00:33:02,660 --> 00:33:03,410
You can’t!

569
00:33:03,790 --> 00:33:06,730
You are forbidden to mention singing operas in the Cheng family.

570
00:33:08,540 --> 00:33:09,370
Everybody come here.

571
00:33:10,840 --> 00:33:11,380
Come here.

572
00:33:15,220 --> 00:33:16,730
You are a lady of the Cheng family,

573
00:33:16,940 --> 00:33:18,210
you are from a respectable family,

574
00:33:18,330 --> 00:33:20,100
don’t learn those coquettish things.

575
00:33:20,690 --> 00:33:21,410
Fengtai,

576
00:33:21,740 --> 00:33:22,250
come here.

577
00:33:22,350 --> 00:33:22,970
No!

578
00:33:28,060 --> 00:33:29,610
Go away, I’m not going!

579
00:33:30,260 --> 00:33:31,370
Look, look,

580
00:33:31,700 --> 00:33:33,450
what did you teach a good child?

581
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:34,810
As I said,

582
00:33:35,100 --> 00:33:36,090
actresses are no good for marriage.

583
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,490
They corrupt moral standards of the family.

584
00:33:37,740 --> 00:33:38,730
Now

585
00:33:38,740 --> 00:33:40,090
the devil has entered the door.

586
00:33:42,850 --> 00:33:44,170
Your mother is keen on going to the opera.

587
00:33:45,020 --> 00:33:46,410
Why can’t I do it?

588
00:33:47,260 --> 00:33:48,450
You are different.

589
00:33:48,980 --> 00:33:50,690
You are a daughter-in-law of the Cheng family.

590
00:33:50,780 --> 00:33:52,010
As we agreed back then,

591
00:33:52,940 --> 00:33:54,450
you must quit singing opera

592
00:33:54,940 --> 00:33:56,770
if you marry into the Cheng family.

593
00:33:59,740 --> 00:34:01,090
That’s indeed what we agreed back then.

594
00:34:02,740 --> 00:34:03,770
But I’ve regretted it.

595
00:34:09,170 --> 00:34:09,929
Chunxuan,

596
00:34:11,530 --> 00:34:13,449
I thought we had true love.

597
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:16,409
If I don’t truly love you,

598
00:34:17,050 --> 00:34:18,969
do I have to be your concubine?

599
00:34:19,860 --> 00:34:22,290
Do I have to abandon the troupe and stay at home?

600
00:34:24,179 --> 00:34:25,409
Fengtai is so young.

601
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:27,770
Where are you going if not staying at home?

602
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:28,969
How can you do that?

603
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:31,330
I,

604
00:34:32,380 --> 00:34:33,330
in order to marry you,

605
00:34:33,570 --> 00:34:34,520
how much effort did I put in?

606
00:34:35,179 --> 00:34:35,770
Yes,

607
00:34:37,460 --> 00:34:39,250
Master Cheng, in order to marry me,

608
00:34:39,780 --> 00:34:41,170
you were subject to a lot of domestic disciplines,

609
00:34:42,460 --> 00:34:43,449
but after that,

610
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:45,730
you are still living your life as a young master.

611
00:34:46,020 --> 00:34:47,409
What do you want me to do?

612
00:34:47,659 --> 00:34:49,489
To wander around the world with your troupe?

613
00:34:54,380 --> 00:34:55,929
I want you to set me free.

614
00:34:58,910 --> 00:35:00,550
I can’t live such a life anymore.

615
00:35:12,940 --> 00:35:13,530
Mom.

616
00:35:18,060 --> 00:35:19,250
Mom, where are you going?

617
00:35:20,620 --> 00:35:22,210
Mommy has left the stage,

618
00:35:22,980 --> 00:35:24,090
kept walking,

619
00:35:24,820 --> 00:35:26,370
and lost myself on the way.

620
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:31,330
Now I have to go back to find myself again.

621
00:35:39,740 --> 00:35:41,490
You are the only one I feel guilt to.

622
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:46,130
You are still so young.

623
00:36:00,580 --> 00:36:01,410
Be good.

624
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:16,850
Mom.

625
00:36:17,940 --> 00:36:18,570
Mom!

626
00:36:20,130 --> 00:36:22,050
Mom, mom, where are you going?

627
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:23,170
Mom!

628
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:24,450
Mom, come back!

629
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:25,570
Mom!

630
00:36:25,580 --> 00:36:27,290
Many years later, it often occurs to me that

631
00:36:27,300 --> 00:36:28,250
Mom, don’t go!

632
00:36:28,260 --> 00:36:29,570
perhaps she came to the family

633
00:36:30,300 --> 00:36:32,330
just to give my younger brother to us.

634
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:33,290
Mom, don’t go!

635
00:36:33,300 --> 00:36:34,730
-A woman like Chunxuan
-Mom!

636
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:37,090
-does not belong to my father,
-Mom!

637
00:36:37,410 --> 00:36:38,770
still less to the Cheng family.

638
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:41,610
-She belongs to herself.
-Mom, come back!

639
00:36:42,060 --> 00:36:43,850
Did they never see each other again?

640
00:36:45,580 --> 00:36:46,850
But my younger brother

641
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:50,050
has never forgotten her in his heart.

642
00:36:52,860 --> 00:36:53,490
Then

643
00:36:54,460 --> 00:36:56,330
why did he never bring it up?

644
00:36:58,580 --> 00:37:00,090
The mother-son bond is love,

645
00:37:01,180 --> 00:37:02,450
and abandonment is hate.

646
00:37:04,090 --> 00:37:05,250
The interwoven love and hate

647
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:07,610
has left him speechless.

648
00:37:20,220 --> 00:37:22,730
It seems I’ve really hurt him this time.

649
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:32,010
Chunxuan has been away for over 20 years.

650
00:37:33,580 --> 00:37:34,690
Whether love or hate,

651
00:37:35,420 --> 00:37:36,530
it’s time to forget.

652
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:40,890
You are so nice to my younger brother,

653
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:44,290
he’ll get to know sooner or later

654
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:47,010
that you are the one closest to him.

655
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:04,290
You make me sleep in the same room with the ancestor?

656
00:38:04,500 --> 00:38:06,090
My father will keep you company.

657
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:09,250
Mr. Cheng,

658
00:38:09,780 --> 00:38:10,850
Don’t you want somewhere clean?

659
00:38:11,060 --> 00:38:12,490
This is the cleanest place.

660
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:13,090
Come on.

661
00:38:15,180 --> 00:38:15,650
Take a seat.

662
00:38:20,700 --> 00:38:22,370
This place is “squeaky clean” indeed.

663
00:38:33,250 --> 00:38:33,970
Mr. Cheng,

664
00:38:35,540 --> 00:38:37,970
how did you get booted out by your wife?

665
00:38:38,820 --> 00:38:39,930
Did she hit you?

666
00:38:40,940 --> 00:38:42,010
Why?

667
00:38:43,020 --> 00:38:44,170
Are you still a human being?

668
00:38:45,660 --> 00:38:47,930
Can’t you take the slightest bit of cue from me?

669
00:38:49,220 --> 00:38:50,490
Such a tongue-in-cheek grin.

670
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:51,930
Is this a good thing?

671
00:38:57,730 --> 00:38:58,780
To tell you the truth,

672
00:38:59,260 --> 00:38:59,970
I

673
00:39:00,180 --> 00:39:01,450
always think you are

674
00:39:01,460 --> 00:39:02,920
a man who can do great things.

675
00:39:03,460 --> 00:39:05,730
You are just like the famous business theorist

676
00:39:06,100 --> 00:39:07,090
and the capable statesman in the opera scripts.

677
00:39:08,220 --> 00:39:10,070
You have both the brain

678
00:39:10,700 --> 00:39:12,570
and the means.

679
00:39:13,100 --> 00:39:13,810
You

680
00:39:13,940 --> 00:39:15,450
are just dragged down by your family.

681
00:39:15,820 --> 00:39:17,210
The Cao family, the Fan family,

682
00:39:17,220 --> 00:39:19,650
your wife’s brother and your nephew all count on you.

683
00:39:20,780 --> 00:39:22,490
Your heart is being dragged old.

684
00:39:22,860 --> 00:39:24,750
From now on, be footloose and fancy-free

685
00:39:24,900 --> 00:39:27,010
and do whatever you like.

686
00:39:27,620 --> 00:39:28,450
As I see it,

687
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:30,370
this is a great blessing.

688
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:34,550
Although what you said doesn’t make sense,

689
00:39:35,860 --> 00:39:36,730
it’s not totally wrong either.

690
00:39:37,980 --> 00:39:39,010
Most of the times,

691
00:39:41,660 --> 00:39:43,330
I desperately want to make money,

692
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:46,570
but I dare not take the risk and go for broke.

693
00:39:47,580 --> 00:39:48,650
With the two conflicting thoughts holding me back,

694
00:39:49,260 --> 00:39:50,210
it’s really painful.

695
00:39:52,420 --> 00:39:53,850
Once you carry

696
00:39:55,100 --> 00:39:56,650
the responsibility of family on your shoulders,

697
00:39:57,780 --> 00:39:59,370
you can’t put it down anymore.

698
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:01,490
I don’t get it.

699
00:40:02,660 --> 00:40:03,570
But I know

700
00:40:04,220 --> 00:40:05,810
whoever holds me back from singing operas

701
00:40:06,020 --> 00:40:06,930
is a burden

702
00:40:07,180 --> 00:40:07,930
which be dropped.

703
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:09,570
Yes.

704
00:40:10,420 --> 00:40:12,360
Apart from operas and your life,

705
00:40:12,500 --> 00:40:13,410
you can drop everything else.

706
00:40:15,460 --> 00:40:16,670
If I can’t sing operas,

707
00:40:17,140 --> 00:40:18,330
I can even give up my life,

708
00:40:18,620 --> 00:40:20,450
let alone wife, children,

709
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:21,410
kith and kin.

710
00:40:22,180 --> 00:40:23,970
I can’t let them drag me down.

711
00:40:25,220 --> 00:40:26,370
Doesn’t your father have a family too?

712
00:40:26,940 --> 00:40:27,930
And Hou Yukui,

713
00:40:28,320 --> 00:40:28,930
isn’t he

714
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:30,290
a top-notch opera singer too?

715
00:40:30,940 --> 00:40:32,610
Hou Yukui, Mr. Hou,

716
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,530
in order to support his big family,

717
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:36,090
tried desperately to sing operas.

718
00:40:36,100 --> 00:40:36,990
When he got injured,

719
00:40:37,060 --> 00:40:38,070
in order to ease his pain,

720
00:40:38,090 --> 00:40:40,180
he had no choice but to smoke opium.

721
00:40:40,580 --> 00:40:42,210
Otherwise given his skills,

722
00:40:42,220 --> 00:40:43,770
he can still take the stage and sing even to this day.

723
00:40:43,780 --> 00:40:44,570
As to my father,

724
00:40:44,580 --> 00:40:45,530
still less needless to say…

725
00:40:45,540 --> 00:40:46,730
Enough, enough, enough.

726
00:40:49,740 --> 00:40:51,610
I’m really feeling so bad.

727
00:40:52,620 --> 00:40:53,850
Can’t you take back your schadenfreude

728
00:40:53,860 --> 00:40:54,810
a bit?

729
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:56,450
It’s obviously a good thing,

730
00:40:56,540 --> 00:40:57,930
but you don’t want others to be happy for you.

731
00:41:01,020 --> 00:41:01,610
Mr. Cheng,

732
00:41:01,980 --> 00:41:04,250
why on earth did you quarrel?

733
00:41:06,060 --> 00:41:06,970
Get out of here!

734
00:41:12,900 --> 00:41:13,810
Go, go, go.

735
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:15,010
Go and get a basin

736
00:41:15,020 --> 00:41:16,050
of scalding water for me to wash my feet.

737
00:41:16,970 --> 00:41:18,130
I always worry about you,

738
00:41:18,370 --> 00:41:19,570
and it’s your turn to repay me.

739
00:41:19,700 --> 00:41:21,050
I’ll tell you when You serve me comfortable.

740
00:41:22,060 --> 00:41:22,810
Just a moment.

741
00:41:24,780 --> 00:41:26,940
(Chunxuan)

742
00:41:43,220 --> 00:41:43,850
Mrs. Cheng,

743
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:44,970
did you ask for me?

744
00:41:46,380 --> 00:41:48,260
I’ve had a good look at this envelope

745
00:41:48,600 --> 00:41:50,050
and found the paper very familiar.

746
00:41:50,380 --> 00:41:51,440
Please have a look as well.

747
00:41:59,300 --> 00:42:00,280
It looks very much like the paper

748
00:42:00,460 --> 00:42:01,970
imported from the Soviet Union.

749
00:42:03,020 --> 00:42:04,850
It’s used more often in Mukden.

750
00:42:05,540 --> 00:42:07,840
Do you suspect the old lady is in Mukden?

751
00:42:10,260 --> 00:42:12,090
I suppose this letter was written not long ago.

752
00:42:12,100 --> 00:42:13,130
Maybe it’s still not too late.

753
00:42:14,220 --> 00:42:15,650
Go to Mukden tomorrow

754
00:42:15,660 --> 00:42:17,300
and see if you can find anything.

755
00:42:19,140 --> 00:42:19,810
Keep it with you.

756
00:42:19,820 --> 00:42:20,580
Don’t lose it.

757
00:42:22,260 --> 00:42:22,730
OK.

758
00:42:23,260 --> 00:42:24,170
Rest assured, Mr. Cheng.

759
00:42:24,260 --> 00:42:24,850
Go quickly.

760
00:42:42,180 --> 00:42:43,730
Jiang Mengping

761
00:42:44,420 --> 00:42:45,530
has been like this ever since she was a kid.

762
00:42:46,260 --> 00:42:48,570
She likes meddling in others’ household affairs.

763
00:42:49,340 --> 00:42:50,090
Just wait and see,

764
00:42:50,620 --> 00:42:52,130
with her staying by your wife’s side,

765
00:42:52,500 --> 00:42:55,050
you’ll have to continue your bad luck.

766
00:42:57,580 --> 00:42:59,650
Can’t you wish me well?

767
00:43:00,380 --> 00:43:01,360
But Mr. Cheng,

768
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:04,250
you are a gigolo who made a fortune

769
00:43:04,260 --> 00:43:05,210
with your wife’s backing.

770
00:43:06,100 --> 00:43:07,810
You relied on Mrs. Mammon’s maiden family

771
00:43:07,820 --> 00:43:08,690
to make a comeback.

772
00:43:08,700 --> 00:43:09,690
Isn’t this true?

773
00:43:09,980 --> 00:43:11,090
You are not wronged.

774
00:43:11,820 --> 00:43:13,570
What are you angry about?

775
00:43:15,620 --> 00:43:17,490
I just can’t make it clear to you.

776
00:43:19,900 --> 00:43:21,210
Even if I can,

777
00:43:21,220 --> 00:43:22,050
you won’t understand!

778
00:43:27,180 --> 00:43:27,810
What’s more,

779
00:43:30,260 --> 00:43:32,530
that’s not the only thing I’m angry about.

780
00:43:41,260 --> 00:43:43,250
You are even keeping a picture of me secretly.

781
00:43:43,380 --> 00:43:44,330
Are you blind?

782
00:43:45,260 --> 00:43:46,570
This is my mother!
